Title: Animal Print Furry Hair Band (Various Colours)
Body: It doesn't need pointing out that this fur is faux, partly because the only creature that would produce black and pink fur would be a Muppet (Note: no Muppets were harmed in the making of these head bands).
Tags: animal print, fur, hair band, head band, leopard, pink

Title: Belt Buckle - Silver Bulldog "Boss
Body: Looks like Bruce Springsteen might have a fight on his hands as to who really is 'The Boss'. After all, this dog seem pretty convinced it's him. If you feel that the boss is actually you, what better way to say it than with a very cool belt buckle?

Title: Belt Buckle - Skull and Cross Gold and Black Adornment
Body: Featuring the mandatory mixture of skulls and crosses, this buckle is the  perfect way to jazz up one's common or garden variety belt! Heavy duty and oh so cool, perfect for adding a dash of rock to an outfit.

Title: Black and Blue Skull Arm Length Fingerless Gloves
Body:
Helping to keep your hands snug in all their stripey glory, these elbow length fingerless gloves are available in a variety of different colours, and skull types (hence forth known as Pirate Skull, Cheery Skull and Mutant skull). This one is Pirate Skull me hearties.

Uni-sex, one size fits all. Also available in regular length.

Body: Black and pink checked skater style wallet with chain. Especially hot pink.
